{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I love video games."},{"time":3000,"text":"I'm also slightly in awe of them."},{"time":6000,"text":"I'm in awe of their power"},{"time":8000,"text":"in terms of imagination, in terms of technology,"},{"time":10000,"text":"in terms of concept."},{"time":12000,"text":"But I think, above all,"},{"time":14000,"text":"I'm in awe at their power"},{"time":16000,"text":"to motivate, to compel us,"},{"time":19000,"text":"to transfix us,"},{"time":21000,"text":"like really nothing else we've ever invented"},{"time":24000,"text":"has quite done before."},{"time":26000,"text":"And I think that we can learn some pretty amazing things"},{"time":29000,"text":"by looking at how we do this."},{"time":31000,"text":"And in particular, I think we can learn things"},{"time":33000,"text":"about learning."},{"time":36000,"text":"Now the video games industry"},{"time":38000,"text":"is far and away the fastest growing"},{"time":40000,"text":"of all modern media."},{"time":42000,"text":"From about 10 billion in 1990,"},{"time":44000,"text":"it's worth 50 billion dollars globally today,"},{"time":47000,"text":"and it shows no sign of slowing down."},{"time":50000,"text":"In four years' time,"},{"time":52000,"text":"it's estimated it'll be worth over 80 billion dollars."},{"time":55000,"text":"That's about three times the recorded music industry."},{"time":58000,"text":"This is pretty stunning,"},{"time":60000,"text":"but I don't think it's the most telling statistic of all."},{"time":63000,"text":"The thing that really amazes me"},{"time":65000,"text":"is that, today,"},{"time":67000,"text":"people spend about"},{"time":69000,"text":"eight billion real dollars a year"},{"time":72000,"text":"buying virtual items"},{"time":74000,"text":"that only exist"},{"time":76000,"text":"inside video games."},{"time":79000,"text":"This is a screenshot from the virtual game world, Entropia Universe."},{"time":82000,"text":"Earlier this year,"},{"time":84000,"text":"a virtual asteroid in it"},{"time":86000,"text":"sold for 330,000 real dollars."},{"time":90000,"text":"And this"},{"time":92000,"text":"is a Titan class ship"},{"time":95000,"text":"in the space game, EVE Online."},{"time":97000,"text":"And this virtual object"},{"time":99000,"text":"takes 200 real people"},{"time":101000,"text":"about 56 days of real time to build,"},{"time":104000,"text":"plus countless thousands of hours"},{"time":107000,"text":"of effort before that."},{"time":109000,"text":"And yet, many of these get built."},{"time":112000,"text":"At the other end of the scale,"},{"time":114000,"text":"the game Farmville that you may well have heard of,"},{"time":117000,"text":"has 70 million players"},{"time":119000,"text":"around the world"},{"time":121000,"text":"and most of these players"},{"time":123000,"text":"are playing it almost every day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125000,"text":"This may all sound"},{"time":127000,"text":"really quite alarming to some people,"},{"time":129000,"text":"an index of something worrying"},{"time":131000,"text":"or wrong in society."},{"time":133000,"text":"But we're here for the good news,"},{"time":135000,"text":"and the good news is"},{"time":137000,"text":"that I think we can explore"},{"time":139000,"text":"why this very real human effort,"},{"time":142000,"text":"this very intense generation of value, is occurring."},{"time":146000,"text":"And by answering that question,"},{"time":148000,"text":"I think we can take something"},{"time":150000,"text":"extremely powerful away."},{"time":152000,"text":"And I think the most interesting way"},{"time":154000,"text":"to think about how all this is going on"},{"time":156000,"text":"is in terms of rewards."},{"time":158000,"text":"And specifically, it's in terms"},{"time":161000,"text":"of the very intense emotional rewards"},{"time":163000,"text":"that playing games offers to people"},{"time":165000,"text":"both individually"},{"time":167000,"text":"and collectively."},{"time":169000,"text":"Now if we look at what's going on in someone's head"},{"time":171000,"text":"when they are being engaged,"},{"time":173000,"text":"two quite different processes are occurring."},{"time":176000,"text":"On the one hand, there's the wanting processes."},{"time":179000,"text":"This is a bit like ambition and drive -- I'm going to do that. I'm going to work hard."},{"time":182000,"text":"On the other hand, there's the liking processes,"},{"time":184000,"text":"fun and affection"},{"time":186000,"text":"and delight"},{"time":188000,"text":"and an enormous flying beast with an orc on the back."},{"time":190000,"text":"It's a really great image. It's pretty cool."},{"time":192000,"text":"It's from the game World of Warcraft with more than 10 million players globally,"},{"time":195000,"text":"one of whom is me, another of whom is my wife."},{"time":198000,"text":"And this kind of a world,"},{"time":200000,"text":"this vast flying beast you can ride around,"},{"time":202000,"text":"shows why games are so very good"},{"time":204000,"text":"at doing both the wanting and the liking."},{"time":207000,"text":"Because it's very powerful. It's pretty awesome."},{"time":209000,"text":"It gives you great powers."},{"time":211000,"text":"Your ambition is satisfied, but it's very beautiful."},{"time":214000,"text":"It's a very great pleasure to fly around."},{"time":217000,"text":"And so these combine to form"},{"time":219000,"text":"a very intense emotional engagement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221000,"text":"But this isn't the really interesting stuff."},{"time":224000,"text":"The really interesting stuff about virtuality"},{"time":226000,"text":"is what you can measure with it."},{"time":228000,"text":"Because what you can measure in virtuality"},{"time":231000,"text":"is everything."},{"time":233000,"text":"Every single thing that every single person"},{"time":235000,"text":"who's ever played in a game has ever done can be measured."},{"time":238000,"text":"The biggest games in the world today"},{"time":240000,"text":"are measuring more than one billion points of data"},{"time":244000,"text":"about their players, about what everybody does --"},{"time":246000,"text":"far more detail than you'd ever get from any website."},{"time":249000,"text":"And this allows something very special"},{"time":252000,"text":"to happen in games."},{"time":254000,"text":"It's something called the reward schedule."},{"time":257000,"text":"And by this, I mean looking"},{"time":259000,"text":"at what millions upon millions of people have done"},{"time":261000,"text":"and carefully calibrating the rate,"},{"time":263000,"text":"the nature, the type, the intensity of rewards in games"},{"time":266000,"text":"to keep them engaged"},{"time":268000,"text":"over staggering amounts of time and effort."},{"time":271000,"text":"Now, to try and explain this"},{"time":273000,"text":"in sort of real terms,"},{"time":276000,"text":"I want to talk about a kind of task"},{"time":278000,"text":"that might fall to you in so many games."},{"time":280000,"text":"Go and get a certain amount of a certain little game-y item."},{"time":283000,"text":"Let's say, for the sake of argument,"},{"time":285000,"text":"my mission is to get 15 pies"},{"time":288000,"text":"and I can get 15 pies"},{"time":291000,"text":"by killing these cute, little monsters."},{"time":293000,"text":"Simple game quest."},{"time":295000,"text":"Now you can think about this, if you like,"},{"time":297000,"text":"as a problem about boxes."},{"time":299000,"text":"I've got to keep opening boxes."},{"time":301000,"text":"I don't know what's inside them until I open them."},{"time":304000,"text":"And I go around opening box after box until I've got 15 pies."},{"time":307000,"text":"Now, if you take a game like Warcraft,"},{"time":309000,"text":"you can think about it, if you like,"},{"time":311000,"text":"as a great box-opening effort."},{"time":314000,"text":"The game's just trying to get people to open about a million boxes,"},{"time":317000,"text":"getting better and better stuff in them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319000,"text":"This sounds immensely boring"},{"time":322000,"text":"but games are able"},{"time":324000,"text":"to make this process"},{"time":326000,"text":"incredibly compelling."},{"time":328000,"text":"And the way they do this"},{"time":330000,"text":"is through a combination of probability and data."},{"time":333000,"text":"Let's think about probability."},{"time":335000,"text":"If we want to engage someone"},{"time":337000,"text":"in the process of opening boxes to try and find pies,"},{"time":340000,"text":"we want to make sure it's neither too easy,"},{"time":342000,"text":"nor too difficult, to find a pie."},{"time":344000,"text":"So what do you do? Well, you look at a million people --"},{"time":346000,"text":"no, 100 million people, 100 million box openers --"},{"time":349000,"text":"and you work out, if you make the pie rate"},{"time":352000,"text":"about 25 percent --"},{"time":354000,"text":"that's neither too frustrating, nor too easy."},{"time":357000,"text":"It keeps people engaged."},{"time":359000,"text":"But of course, that's not all you do -- there's 15 pies."},{"time":362000,"text":"Now, I could make a game called Piecraft,"},{"time":364000,"text":"where all you had to do was get a million pies"},{"time":366000,"text":"or a thousand pies."},{"time":368000,"text":"That would be very boring."},{"time":370000,"text":"Fifteen is a pretty optimal number."},{"time":372000,"text":"You find that -- you know, between five and 20"},{"time":374000,"text":"is about the right number for keeping people going."},{"time":376000,"text":"But we don't just have pies in the boxes."},{"time":378000,"text":"There's 100 percent up here."},{"time":380000,"text":"And what we do is make sure that every time a box is opened,"},{"time":383000,"text":"there's something in it, some little reward"},{"time":385000,"text":"that keeps people progressing and engaged."},{"time":387000,"text":"In most adventure games,"},{"time":389000,"text":"it's a little bit in-game currency, a little bit experience."},{"time":392000,"text":"But we don't just do that either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394000,"text":"We also say there's going to be loads of other items"},{"time":396000,"text":"of varying qualities and levels of excitement."},{"time":398000,"text":"There's going to be a 10 percent chance you get a pretty good item."},{"time":401000,"text":"There's going to be a 0.1 percent chance"},{"time":403000,"text":"you get an absolutely awesome item."},{"time":406000,"text":"And each of these rewards is carefully calibrated to the item."},{"time":409000,"text":"And also, we say,"},{"time":411000,"text":"\"Well, how many monsters? Should I have the entire world full of a billion monsters?\""},{"time":414000,"text":"No, we want one or two monsters on the screen at any one time."},{"time":417000,"text":"So I'm drawn on. It's not too easy, not too difficult."},{"time":420000,"text":"So all this is very powerful."},{"time":422000,"text":"But we're in virtuality. These aren't real boxes."},{"time":425000,"text":"So we can do"},{"time":427000,"text":"some rather amazing things."},{"time":429000,"text":"We notice, looking at all these people opening boxes,"},{"time":433000,"text":"that when people get to about 13 out of 15 pies,"},{"time":436000,"text":"their perception shifts, they start to get a bit bored, a bit testy."},{"time":439000,"text":"They're not rational about probability."},{"time":441000,"text":"They think this game is unfair."},{"time":443000,"text":"It's not giving me my last two pies. I'm going to give up."},{"time":445000,"text":"If they're real boxes, there's not much we can do,"},{"time":447000,"text":"but in a game we can just say, \"Right, well."},{"time":449000,"text":"When you get to 13 pies, you've got 75 percent chance of getting a pie now.\""},{"time":453000,"text":"Keep you engaged. Look at what people do --"},{"time":455000,"text":"adjust the world to match their expectation."},{"time":457000,"text":"Our games don't always do this."},{"time":459000,"text":"And one thing they certainly do at the moment"},{"time":461000,"text":"is if you got a 0.1 percent awesome item,"},{"time":464000,"text":"they make very sure another one doesn't appear for a certain length of time"},{"time":467000,"text":"to keep the value, to keep it special."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469000,"text":"And the point is really"},{"time":471000,"text":"that we evolved to be satisfied by the world"},{"time":473000,"text":"in particular ways."},{"time":475000,"text":"Over tens and hundreds of thousands of years,"},{"time":478000,"text":"we evolved to find certain things stimulating,"},{"time":480000,"text":"and as very intelligent, civilized beings,"},{"time":482000,"text":"we're enormously stimulated by problem solving and learning."},{"time":485000,"text":"But now, we can reverse engineer that"},{"time":487000,"text":"and build worlds"},{"time":489000,"text":"that expressly tick our evolutionary boxes."},{"time":492000,"text":"So what does all this mean in practice?"},{"time":494000,"text":"Well, I've come up"},{"time":496000,"text":"with seven things"},{"time":498000,"text":"that, I think, show"},{"time":500000,"text":"how you can take these lessons from games"},{"time":502000,"text":"and use them outside of games."},{"time":505000,"text":"The first one is very simple:"},{"time":507000,"text":"experience bars measuring progress --"},{"time":509000,"text":"something that's been talked about brilliantly"},{"time":511000,"text":"by people like Jesse Schell earlier this year."},{"time":514000,"text":"It's already been done at the University of Indiana in the States, among other places."},{"time":517000,"text":"It's the simple idea that instead of grading people incrementally"},{"time":520000,"text":"in little bits and pieces,"},{"time":522000,"text":"you give them one profile character avatar"},{"time":524000,"text":"which is constantly progressing"},{"time":526000,"text":"in tiny, tiny, tiny little increments which they feel are their own."},{"time":529000,"text":"And everything comes towards that,"},{"time":531000,"text":"and they watch it creeping up, and they own that as it goes along."}]},{"cues":[{"time":534000,"text":"Second, multiple long and short-term aims --"},{"time":536000,"text":"5,000 pies, boring,"},{"time":538000,"text":"15 pies, interesting."},{"time":540000,"text":"So, you give people"},{"time":542000,"text":"lots and lots of different tasks."},{"time":544000,"text":"You say, it's about"},{"time":546000,"text":"doing 10 of these questions,"},{"time":548000,"text":"but another task"},{"time":550000,"text":"is turning up to 20 classes on time,"},{"time":552000,"text":"but another task is collaborating with other people,"},{"time":555000,"text":"another task is showing you're working five times,"},{"time":558000,"text":"another task is hitting this particular target."},{"time":560000,"text":"You break things down into these calibrated slices"},{"time":563000,"text":"that people can choose and do in parallel"},{"time":565000,"text":"to keep them engaged"},{"time":567000,"text":"and that you can use to point them"},{"time":569000,"text":"towards individually beneficial activities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":573000,"text":"Third, you reward effort."},{"time":575000,"text":"It's your 100 percent factor. Games are brilliant at this."},{"time":578000,"text":"Every time you do something, you get credit; you get a credit for trying."},{"time":581000,"text":"You don't punish failure. You reward every little bit of effort --"},{"time":584000,"text":"a little bit of gold, a little bit of credit. You've done 20 questions -- tick."},{"time":587000,"text":"It all feeds in as minute reinforcement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":590000,"text":"Fourth, feedback."},{"time":592000,"text":"This is absolutely crucial,"},{"time":594000,"text":"and virtuality is dazzling at delivering this."},{"time":596000,"text":"If you look at some of the most intractable problems in the world today"},{"time":599000,"text":"that we've been hearing amazing things about,"},{"time":601000,"text":"it's very, very hard for people to learn"},{"time":604000,"text":"if they cannot link consequences to actions."},{"time":607000,"text":"Pollution, global warming, these things --"},{"time":609000,"text":"the consequences are distant in time and space."},{"time":611000,"text":"It's very hard to learn, to feel a lesson."},{"time":613000,"text":"But if you can model things for people,"},{"time":615000,"text":"if you can give things to people that they can manipulate"},{"time":617000,"text":"and play with and where the feedback comes,"},{"time":619000,"text":"then they can learn a lesson, they can see,"},{"time":621000,"text":"they can move on, they can understand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624000,"text":"And fifth,"},{"time":626000,"text":"the element of uncertainty."},{"time":628000,"text":"Now this is the neurological goldmine,"},{"time":631000,"text":"if you like,"},{"time":633000,"text":"because a known reward"},{"time":635000,"text":"excites people,"},{"time":637000,"text":"but what really gets them going"},{"time":639000,"text":"is the uncertain reward,"},{"time":641000,"text":"the reward pitched at the right level of uncertainty,"},{"time":643000,"text":"that they didn't quite know whether they were going to get it or not."},{"time":646000,"text":"The 25 percent. This lights the brain up."},{"time":649000,"text":"And if you think about"},{"time":651000,"text":"using this in testing,"},{"time":653000,"text":"in just introducing control elements of randomness"},{"time":655000,"text":"in all forms of testing and training,"},{"time":657000,"text":"you can transform the levels of people's engagement"},{"time":659000,"text":"by tapping into this very powerful"},{"time":661000,"text":"evolutionary mechanism."},{"time":663000,"text":"When we don't quite predict something perfectly,"},{"time":665000,"text":"we get really excited about it."},{"time":667000,"text":"We just want to go back and find out more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":669000,"text":"As you probably know, the neurotransmitter"},{"time":671000,"text":"associated with learning is called dopamine."},{"time":673000,"text":"It's associated with reward-seeking behavior."},{"time":676000,"text":"And something very exciting is just beginning to happen"},{"time":679000,"text":"in places like the University of Bristol in the U.K.,"},{"time":682000,"text":"where we are beginning to be able to model mathematically"},{"time":685000,"text":"dopamine levels in the brain."},{"time":687000,"text":"And what this means is we can predict learning,"},{"time":689000,"text":"we can predict enhanced engagement,"},{"time":692000,"text":"these windows, these windows of time,"},{"time":694000,"text":"in which the learning is taking place at an enhanced level."},{"time":697000,"text":"And two things really flow from this."},{"time":699000,"text":"The first has to do with memory,"},{"time":701000,"text":"that we can find these moments."},{"time":703000,"text":"When someone is more likely to remember,"},{"time":705000,"text":"we can give them a nugget in a window."},{"time":707000,"text":"And the second thing is confidence,"},{"time":709000,"text":"that we can see how game-playing and reward structures"},{"time":711000,"text":"make people braver, make them more willing to take risks,"},{"time":714000,"text":"more willing to take on difficulty,"},{"time":716000,"text":"harder to discourage."},{"time":718000,"text":"This can all seem very sinister."},{"time":720000,"text":"But you know, sort of \"our brains have been manipulated; we're all addicts.\""},{"time":722000,"text":"The word \"addiction\" is thrown around."},{"time":724000,"text":"There are real concerns there."},{"time":726000,"text":"But the biggest neurological turn-on for people"},{"time":728000,"text":"is other people."},{"time":730000,"text":"This is what really excites us."},{"time":733000,"text":"In reward terms, it's not money;"},{"time":735000,"text":"it's not being given cash -- that's nice --"},{"time":738000,"text":"it's doing stuff with our peers,"},{"time":740000,"text":"watching us, collaborating with us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742000,"text":"And I want to tell you a quick story about 1999 --"},{"time":744000,"text":"a video game called EverQuest."},{"time":746000,"text":"And in this video game,"},{"time":748000,"text":"there were two really big dragons, and you had to team up to kill them --"},{"time":751000,"text":"42 people, up to 42 to kill these big dragons."},{"time":754000,"text":"That's a problem"},{"time":756000,"text":"because they dropped two or three decent items."},{"time":759000,"text":"So players addressed this problem"},{"time":762000,"text":"by spontaneously coming up with a system"},{"time":764000,"text":"to motivate each other,"},{"time":766000,"text":"fairly and transparently."},{"time":768000,"text":"What happened was, they paid each other a virtual currency"},{"time":771000,"text":"they called \"dragon kill points.\""},{"time":774000,"text":"And every time you turned up to go on a mission,"},{"time":776000,"text":"you got paid in dragon kill points."},{"time":778000,"text":"They tracked these on a separate website."},{"time":780000,"text":"So they tracked their own private currency,"},{"time":782000,"text":"and then players could bid afterwards"},{"time":784000,"text":"for cool items they wanted --"},{"time":786000,"text":"all organized by the players themselves."},{"time":788000,"text":"Now the staggering system, not just that this worked in EverQuest,"},{"time":791000,"text":"but that today, a decade on,"},{"time":793000,"text":"every single video game in the world with this kind of task"},{"time":796000,"text":"uses a version of this system --"},{"time":798000,"text":"tens of millions of people."},{"time":800000,"text":"And the success rate"},{"time":802000,"text":"is at close to 100 percent."},{"time":804000,"text":"This is a player-developed,"},{"time":806000,"text":"self-enforcing, voluntary currency,"},{"time":809000,"text":"and it's incredibly sophisticated"},{"time":811000,"text":"player behavior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":815000,"text":"And I just want to end by suggesting"},{"time":817000,"text":"a few ways in which these principles"},{"time":819000,"text":"could fan out into the world."},{"time":821000,"text":"Let's start with business."},{"time":823000,"text":"I mean, we're beginning to see some of the big problems"},{"time":825000,"text":"around something like business are"},{"time":827000,"text":"recycling and energy conservation."},{"time":829000,"text":"We're beginning to see the emergence of wonderful technologies"},{"time":831000,"text":"like real-time energy meters."},{"time":833000,"text":"And I just look at this, and I think, yes,"},{"time":835000,"text":"we could take that so much further"},{"time":838000,"text":"by allowing people to set targets"},{"time":840000,"text":"by setting calibrated targets,"},{"time":842000,"text":"by using elements of uncertainty,"},{"time":845000,"text":"by using these multiple targets,"},{"time":847000,"text":"by using a grand, underlying reward and incentive system,"},{"time":850000,"text":"by setting people up"},{"time":852000,"text":"to collaborate in terms of groups, in terms of streets"},{"time":854000,"text":"to collaborate and compete,"},{"time":856000,"text":"to use these very sophisticated"},{"time":858000,"text":"group and motivational mechanics we see."},{"time":860000,"text":"In terms of education,"},{"time":862000,"text":"perhaps most obviously of all,"},{"time":864000,"text":"we can transform how we engage people."},{"time":867000,"text":"We can offer people the grand continuity"},{"time":869000,"text":"of experience and personal investment."},{"time":872000,"text":"We can break things down"},{"time":874000,"text":"into highly calibrated small tasks."},{"time":876000,"text":"We can use calculated randomness."},{"time":878000,"text":"We can reward effort consistently"},{"time":880000,"text":"as everything fields together."},{"time":883000,"text":"And we can use the kind of group behaviors"},{"time":885000,"text":"that we see evolving when people are at play together,"},{"time":888000,"text":"these really quite unprecedentedly complex"},{"time":891000,"text":"cooperative mechanisms."},{"time":893000,"text":"Government, well, one thing that comes to mind"},{"time":895000,"text":"is the U.S. government, among others,"},{"time":898000,"text":"is literally starting to pay people"},{"time":900000,"text":"to lose weight."},{"time":902000,"text":"So we're seeing financial reward being used"},{"time":904000,"text":"to tackle the great issue of obesity."},{"time":906000,"text":"But again, those rewards"},{"time":908000,"text":"could be calibrated so precisely"},{"time":911000,"text":"if we were able to use the vast expertise"},{"time":914000,"text":"of gaming systems to just jack up that appeal,"},{"time":917000,"text":"to take the data, to take the observations,"},{"time":919000,"text":"of millions of human hours"},{"time":921000,"text":"and plow that feedback"},{"time":923000,"text":"into increasing engagement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":925000,"text":"And in the end, it's this word, \"engagement,\""},{"time":928000,"text":"that I want to leave you with."},{"time":930000,"text":"It's about how individual engagement"},{"time":932000,"text":"can be transformed"},{"time":934000,"text":"by the psychological and the neurological lessons"},{"time":937000,"text":"we can learn from watching people that are playing games."},{"time":940000,"text":"But it's also about collective engagement"},{"time":943000,"text":"and about the unprecedented laboratory"},{"time":946000,"text":"for observing what makes people tick"},{"time":948000,"text":"and work and play and engage"},{"time":950000,"text":"on a grand scale in games."},{"time":953000,"text":"And if we can look at these things and learn from them"},{"time":956000,"text":"and see how to turn them outwards,"},{"time":958000,"text":"then I really think we have something quite revolutionary on our hands."}]},{"cues":[{"time":961000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":963000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}